item.title: About Me
item.description: Degrees MILLIKIN UNIVERSITY (2021) B.S. in Biochemistry Minors: Biology, Chemistry, Psychology, Mathematics NORTHWESTERN UNIVERSITY (Expected Jan. 2025) M.S. in Data Science Personal Fascinations I find great joy in the company of my friends and family, cherishing those close connections. My interests span a wide range, encompassing a love for science, mathematics, and data, as well as a creative side that comes alive through sketching, drawing, and painting. Gaming is a significant part of my leisure time, with Xbox, Nintendo Switch, and DS being my platforms of choice.
